HEADWORD: Roughwork
<hw>Rough"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To work over
coarsely, without regard to nicety, smoothness, or finish.</def>
<rj><au>Moxon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

